{
  "stem": "19210.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 355.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And also they didn't care for the fact that there were rumors that the Nazis, the German Army, may even invade Portugal.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there was always some maneuvers going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Of course, that never materialized, but there was always a talk amongst the-- the people that, well, there's a possibility that-- that the war will affect us ultimately because they'll come in.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the government of Portugal, Salazar, they had sent troops to different parts of Portugal to the frontiers and to the-- for special training, et cetera, et cetera, but it never-- nothing ever happened.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I heard already, and particularly because I was also a Jew-- in the synagogue there was-- there was-- there was not just natives of Portugal, but you would see there was a few group of Polish Jews that I remember from Lotz, L-O-T-Z.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I remember they used to manufacture wool sweaters and sell them in the summer in the beaches of-- outside Lisbon.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so they spoke already Portuguese, they learned the language.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you would hear them talk about what goes on, the-- the problems with the-- with the-- the Nazis in exterminating the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, one of the reasons that I left Portugal was because I wanted to go to-- to Eretz, to Palestine, and to join the army and go and fight the Nazis-- me and my brother, God rest his soul, my cousin, and several other members of the Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was one of the main reasons.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We wanted to go and fight the Germans, fight the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't say that I did hear anything about extermination camps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I did not.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
